snippet.title: Pac Man Party 3D Trailer
snippet.description:
Join PacMan's birthday party http://bit.ly/Ah99ib
With over 50 mini-games ad upto 4 players Pac Man Party on Nintendo 3DS wil have you and friends coming back for more and as an added bonus, Pac Man Party 3D comes complete with the original versions of Pac Man, Galaga ad Dig Dug!
